{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "628cc361-f416-4747-ad51-76bfd114cbed",
    "name": "Dining Hall Ifetaya 04: Kwirk at Work",
    "sceneId": "bf8b9872-cbdd-47c6-997c-1cd3ad91bc1e",
    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "7c651433-a914-4599-a4bc-f4ee51b75a07",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "16c876ac-ccab-4774-85b4-303d691ab4a7",
                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "So, Mister Shawn-Shawn - tell to me, what you know of the school thief? Mister Terk, he tells everyone that you Disbarred Bards be the thieves. ",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "701bda6f-832f-4fa7-982f-a4c2b67031db",
                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "<shrug> Then again, Mister Terk, he says many, many things, but not all the things he say be true. You are not the school thief, that I know.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "8d7845f9-5b38-4ad6-b59b-3381a93247d1",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "79f0852e-039a-4c93-b63e-262705a247d8",
                            "text": "Ask How Ifetaya Knows that Shawn is Not the Thief",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d02db1c6-70dd-4619-88fd-327040e30ab9",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "text": "How do you know I am not the thief?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d2814292-78bb-4129-9ac5-680371dbcb21",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "You walk with a wolf and a jackal, Shawn. For now, they walk side by side, snarling at each other. When they part company, it will be your choice of which one to follow.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3ebac243-2966-4b50-a3d2-c73c9b27a02c",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "text": "What does that mean?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8604165d-8cb4-4c9d-978c-e7851662cc54",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It mean, Mister Shawn-Shawn, that you are not yet a thief. You have not chosen your own path. Eshu watches over you, Shawn.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d485f3e5-879e-4a0d-958d-23156b96c1ff",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "text": "Who is Eshu?",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0826eb9d-d9e8-4e89-ad9e-98cbd18f1f83",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "All my answers will just end with more questions from you. For now, be happy to know that what you do really matters. The future comes closer with every step.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "9",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "e3c5c9d2-de01-4f19-80b5-b1d78d157f8e",
                            "text": "Give Ifetaya the Bandages from Lady Moira",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "79ae8615-906c-4353-bfc0-baa32ddc89a5",
                                    "scriptId": "f3605b43-a8fd-45e6-a888-6c03b787f112",
                                    "entryPointId": "3894b528-e9f3-45ff-8760-061056076cfb",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
