                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "b9268ebb-0c31-4d61-89ef-501bbd4a1501",
                            "text": "Ask About Riki",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "648c9c56-9bb4-412e-9af2-40ca4214e4e5",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "4cc48e56-7f61-4887-ad13-4bf879f29b21",
                                    "text": "How are you today, Riki?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "141b864a-a7e8-44f3-bdc7-fb9d99b34358",
                                    "actorId": "4cc48e56-7f61-4887-ad13-4bf879f29b21",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Riki, she is not happy! Thief come kitchen. Thief stole Riki's apples! Riki, she now can make no tarts. No apples.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f726291f-56d6-495c-9491-3d529a7039ec",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "We were to have a lesson on pastry crusts this week, but the thief, he stole all the apples from the barrel. Now there will be no apple tarts until we get many more apples.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "96973977-bec6-41f1-aa5a-71ccf6080223",
                            "text": "Ask About the Thief",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "62b17731-21a4-4aee-954c-2740a6318f77",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "text": "What do you know about the School Thief?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "938af71e-befb-497b-b161-876a64c6dad4",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I know that the thief does not like plantains or quince. The thief, he take a bite of them, but left them all behind. Apples, he took all from the barrel. Now I have to hide away the rest of the apples.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7175b01e-1489-43d4-8a68-f44d8f42226b",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "text": "So the only thing the thief has stolen from here is apples?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "be40f0fe-4a1c-493e-b909-3c67a57e037c",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "So far, yes. But the thief, he must really like apples. He left many cores behind him.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "ea76168b-65fc-489a-a9b2-cb3aa4d0ca0a",
                            "text": "Ask About Apples",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0ce14498-6df7-47d4-a283-0aeef246151f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "text": "The smell of all the cooking is making me hungry again. Could I have an apple to tide me over?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "662d13a6-c36a-4c00-91c1-e8974c0259d1",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Help yourself. The apple bowl is by the south wall for starving students. Just take one for yourself and leave the rest for others.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.inInventory",
                                "propId": "101bea4d-a217-47ee-b808-8c24df1454e8",
                                "sceneId": "a2508b7e-a177-4a96-93bd-4d8ab88dffc4",
                                "has": false
                            },
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "9eb4d6da-bcb1-40db-be12-584b502c810f",
                            "text": "Flirt With Ifetaya",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f5fff677-ffe7-45b6-929e-2bf743d0196d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "text": "So the best cook in all Sardonia is bright and beautiful...",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "23fb5592-464b-4e2d-acb9-2d97c4434e55",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "1c09f5bb-44a0-4330-9520-871b92b6d5c3",
                                    "actorId": "4cc48e56-7f61-4887-ad13-4bf879f29b21",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes! Riki, she be very pretty! Riki, she be very bright! Riki, she be very bestest of cooks!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "29a9e02e-b415-4f24-8851-06121029ed9f",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "4cc48e56-7f61-4887-ad13-4bf879f29b21",
                                    "text": "Riki, she is very modest, too.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "78cd299c-0bf9-4a6f-bf55-5e2dce8b9461",
                                    "actorId": "4cc48e56-7f61-4887-ad13-4bf879f29b21",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes! Riki, she is most modest of all!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "fe6bfc49-b8c5-4290-958e-bb553741c8c0",
                            "text": "Ask for Work",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8fb0d1c6-43bc-46ef-9ea4-ab0f82ad2b85",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "text": "Do you have any work for me today?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
